    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feel without the dealership headache, this is the one for you. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel!",
