    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2019 BMW M2 Competition is a collector-grade specimen, preserved in absolute showroom condition. Finished in Hockenheim Silver Metallic, the paintwork is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating and a clear bra on the front fascia. There are zero rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the black Dakota leather with contrast blue stitching remains taut and supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma; the bolsters show no sign of entry wear, and the carbon fiber trim is pristine. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a full documented history. It has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen rain or track use. This is a rare opportunity to own a modern classic that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
